art-tree-serena-lily-the-inspired-room.jpg 980w, https://theinspiredroom.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/coastal-cottage-christmas-decorating-rattan-bar-cart-tree-serena-lily-the-inspired-room-480x640.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 980px, 100vw\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20980%201307\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://theinspiredroom.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/coastal-cottage-christmas-decorating-rattan-bar-cart-tree-serena-lily-the-inspired-room.jpg 980w, https://theinspiredroom.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/coastal-cottage-christmas-decorating-rattan-bar-cart-tree-serena-lily-the-inspired-room-480x640.jpg 480w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://theinspiredroom.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/coastal-cottage-christmas-decorating-rattan-bar-cart-tree-serena-lily-the-inspired-room.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe other day it felt particularly dark out in the middle of the afternoon so I brought down one of the \u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/4gzbsNR\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003erechargeable lamps\u003c/a\u003e from our \u003ca href=\"https://theinspiredroom.net/my-quick-easy-organized-gift-wrapping-closet/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003egift wrap closet\u003c/a\u003e. I had never considered a lamp here before but it’s made it feel extra cozy and so peaceful. \u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/4gzbsNR\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eRechargeable lamps\u003c/a\u003e or bulbs are perfect for spots like this that don’t have any accessible outlets (or if you don’t want to string a cord from outlet to fixture).\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFor Christmas I placed one of our small trees to \u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/4gfM3ci\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eour kitchen crock\u003c/a\u003e. I tied a small \u003ca hre